\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">선선한 게 찬 음식보다 따뜻한&nbsp;게 좋아지는 날씨입니다. </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">그래서 전자레인지에 밤 음료를 잠깐 데웠어요.</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F25240F4F542B714720BF20\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">여기에 시나몬가루(계피가루) 있으면 뿌려 주면 좋은데 없으니 패스</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F247D3650542B71AF0E85F7\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">하루견과류에 들어있었던 건포도와 건블루베리는 잘게 썰었어요.</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile24.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F25635E4C542B714023DA89\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">그리고 넣어줬답니다. 이렇게 해서 영양음료 밤라떼가 완성되었는데요. 고소하니 정말 맛있네요. 달콤한 건포도와 건블루베리도 넣으니 씹히는 맛도 있는 게 더 맛있는 것 같아요.</p> \n</div>","images":["http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile10.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2666F74C542B71411C7210","http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2640D747542B719A34E056","http://i1.daumcdn.net/